0: SELECT T1.code FROM drivers AS T1 INNER JOIN qualifying AS T2 ON T1.driverId = T2.driverId WHERE T2.raceId = 45 AND T2.q3 LIKE '1:33%'
1: SELECT T1.superhero_name FROM superhero AS T1 INNER JOIN publisher AS T2 ON T1.publisher_id = T2.id WHERE T2.publisher_name = 'Marvel Comics' ORDER BY T1.height_cm DESC
2: SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN T1.DisplayName = 'Mornington' THEN T2.ViewCount ELSE 0 END) - SUM(CASE WHEN T1.DisplayName = 'Amos' THEN T2.ViewCount ELSE 0 END) FROM users AS T1 INNER JOIN posts AS T2 ON T1.Id = T2.OwnerUserId WHERE T1.DisplayName IN ('Mornington', 'Amos')
3: SELECT T1.CommentCount FROM posts AS T1 ORDER BY T1.Score DESC LIMIT 1
4: SELECT T1.name FROM cards AS T1 INNER JOIN foreign_data AS T2 ON T1.uuid = T2.uuid WHERE T1.name = 'Ancestor''s Chosen' AND T2.language = 'Korean'
5: SELECT T1.element FROM atom AS T1 JOIN molecule AS T2 ON T1.molecule_id = T2.molecule_id WHERE T2.label = '-' GROUP BY T1.element ORDER BY COUNT(T1.element) ASC LIMIT 1
6: SELECT count(T1.bond_id) FROM connected AS T1 JOIN atom AS T2 ON T1.atom_id = T2.atom_id WHERE T2.atom_id LIKE 'TR%_19'
7: SELECT T1.element FROM atom AS T1 JOIN molecule AS T2 ON T1.molecule_id = T2.molecule_id WHERE T2.molecule_id = 'TR004'
8: SELECT MAX(T1.`Free Meal Count (Ages 5-17)` * 1.0 / T1.`Enrollment (Ages 5-17)`) FROM frpm AS T1 INNER JOIN satscores AS T2 ON T1.CDSCode = T2.cds WHERE T2.NumGE1500 * 1.0 / T2.NumTstTakr > 0.3
9: SELECT T1.`FRPM Count (K-12)` / T1.`Enrollment (K-12)` FROM frpm AS T1 INNER JOIN schools AS T2 ON T1.CDSCode = T2.CDSCode WHERE T2.SOC = '66' ORDER BY T1.`FRPM Count (K-12)` DESC LIMIT 5
